The evidence with the title 'Barack Obama tells Americans 'don't go to Las Vegas' - Telegraph ' says Feb 3, 2010  ... Speaking about the economy at an event in New Hampshire , mr Obama told Americans: “ when times are tough, you tighten your belts. “ you don't go buying a boat when you can barely pay your mortgage. You don't blow a bunch of cash on Vegas when you're trying to save for college. You prioritise. 
